00:11:50,585 --> 00:11:51,753
Aku berinvestasi.

175
00:11:52,504 --> 00:11:55,465
Dokter Choi adalah dokter yang kompeten.

176
00:11:55,882 --> 00:11:57,634
Dia mengembangkan metodologi bedah baru.

177
00:11:57,717 --> 00:11:59,362
