00:28:58,529 --> 00:28:59,864
Kau mungkin benar.

466
00:29:00,114 --> 00:29:01,157
Tapi...

467
00:29:02,116 --> 00:29:03,993
kasus penculikan ini sangat berbeda

468
00:29:04,076 --> 00:29:05,661
dari kasus biasa.

469
00:29:06,662 --> 00:29:10,416
