470
00:29:10,499 --> 00:29:11,792
yang mengalami reaksi alergi.

471
00:29:12,585 --> 00:29:14,688
Keduanya memberi informasi palsu
dan naik kereta bawah tanah

472
00:29:14,712 --> 00:29:16,338
seolah-olah mereka satu tim.

473
00:29:18,382 --> 00:29:19,800
Dalam kasus ini,

474
00:29:21,802 --> 00:29:23,929
rasanya anak itu yang memimpin.

475
00:29:25,389 --> 00:29:26,932
Mereka seperti bekerja sama.

476
00:29:27,016 --> 00:29:28,017
Kau benar.

477
00:29:28,100 --> 00:29:29,226
Ini menarik.

478
00:29:33,981 --> 00:29:35,149
Aku tak menemukan apa pun.

479
00:29:35,900 --> 00:29:38,986
Tak ada hubungan antara Park Cheol-won
dan Kim Myeong-jun.

480
00:29:39,361 --> 00:29:40,988
Gerakan mereka sangat berbeda.

481
00:29:45,701 --> 00:29:47,828
Omong-omong, keluarga yang aneh.

482
00:29:48,037 --> 00:29:49,079
Apa maksudmu?

483
00:29:50,331 --> 00:29:53,542
