553
00:34:17,222 --> 00:34:18,265
Tidak apa-apa.

554
00:34:19,016 --> 00:34:20,142
Itu yang sebenarnya.

555
00:34:20,434 --> 00:34:22,144
<i>Benar, bukan? Syukurlah.</i>

556
00:34:22,811 --> 00:34:23,896
Selain itu,

557
00:34:24,605 --> 00:34:27,566
kau sudah menyelidiki
hal yang kusebutkan sebelumnya?

558
00:34:27,941 --> 00:34:29,318
<i>Wanita simpanan Dokter Choi.</i>

559
00:34:29,902 --> 00:34:30,903
Tidak.

560
00:34:31,153 --> 00:34:34,281
Dokter Choi punya semua diska kerasnya.

561
00:34:35,032 --> 00:34:36,033
Tapi Dokter Yoon,

562
00:34:37,117 --> 00:34:38,202
omong-omong,

563
00:34:39,661 --> 00:34:41,038
apa kau pernah

564
00:34:42,039 --> 00:34:44,458
melihat simpanannya?

565
00:34:44,833 --> 00:34:45,918
Tentu saja.

566
00:34:46,418 --> 00:34:47,961
Dia sering datang ke rumah sakit,

567
00:34:48,045 --> 00:34:50,631
jadi, aku menemuinya beberapa kali.

568
00:34:51,924 --> 00:34:54,259
Akan sempurna jika ada rekaman.

569
00:34:54,593 --> 00:34:55,886
<i>Mengecewakan sekali.</i>

570
00:34:56,637 --> 00:34:58,972
<i>Omong-omong, Pak Park,
mari makan kapan-kapan.</i>

571
00:34:59,056 --> 00:35:02,267
<i>Aku akan mentraktirmu
makanan lezat di tempat bagus.</i>

572
00:35:02,935 --> 00:35:04,061
Tentu.

573
00:35:04,144 --> 00:35:06,063
<i>Baiklah. Sampai jumpa.</i>

574
00:35:22,329 --> 00:35:23,497
Sampai jumpa.

