673
00:42:13,365 --> 00:42:14,824
Dia menipunya?

674
00:42:15,242 --> 00:42:16,326
Benar, bukan?

675
00:42:17,619 --> 00:42:19,162
Ke arah mana jalan itu membawamu?

676
00:42:19,246 --> 00:42:20,997
- Apa ada jalan keluar?
